olive oil
1 bag Asian Stir-Fry Mix
1 packet beef strips
1 sachet Southeast Asian Spice Blend
1 packet udon noodles
1 bunch coriander
1 sachet Sichuan garlic paste
1 packet Crispy Shallots

Heat olive oil in a frying pan over medium-high heat.
Add stir-fry mix and cook until softened, 3 mins.
Transfer to a bowl and set aside.
Return pan to high heat. Add beef and spice blend and cook until browned, 1-2 mins.

Meanwhile, pierce noodle packet and zap in microwave until steaming, 2 mins.
Chop coriander.

Add Sichuan paste, noodles and veggie mix to the beef.
Toss to combine.
Divide stir-fry between plates and top with coriander and crispy shallots.